{"data":[{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"female","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/f9/01/31326_crt_B858w.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f9/01/31326_crt_B858w.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/f9/01/31326_crt_B858w.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/f9/01/31326_crt_B858w.jpg"},"summary":"明石亘の、双子姉妹の姉。\r\n生徒会長をしているのと同時に、臨時で弓張教会のシスターもやっている。\r\n非常に穏和な性格をしており、みんなから慕われている。","name":"明石小牧","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"明石小牧"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"日文名","v":"明石 小牧"},{"k":"纯假名","v":"あかし こまき"}]},{"key":"性别","value":"女"}],"stat":{"comments":2,"collects":14},"id":31326,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"female","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/d4/36/31327_crt_J8qCl.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d4/36/31327_crt_J8qCl.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/d4/36/31327_crt_J8qCl.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/d4/36/31327_crt_J8qCl.jpg"},"summary":"明石亘の、双子姉妹の妹。\r\n副生徒会長をしており、姉と同じくシスターもやっている。\r\n小牧に比べるとややキツイ性格をしている。\r\n基本的に姉思いだが、兄のことは大っ嫌いである。","name":"明石小沙智","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"明石小沙智"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"k":"日文名","v":"明石 小沙智"},{"k":"纯假名","v":"あかし こさち"}]},{"key":"性别","value":"女"}],"stat":{"comments":5,"collects":12},"id":31327,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":6,"gender":"female","birth_day":29,"birth_year":1938,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/08/b4/24540_crt_1oPvx.jpg?r=1581009610","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/08/b4/24540_crt_1oPvx.jpg?r=1581009610","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/08/b4/24540_crt_1oPvx.jpg?r=1581009610","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/08/b4/24540_crt_1oPvx.jpg?r=1581009610"},"summary":"連合艦隊唯一の工作艦、明石です。\r\nトラック泊地に進出し、前線で損傷した艦艇の修理を担当したわ。トラック泊地が壊滅するその日まで、前線の艦隊を陰で支えたのよ。\r\nよろしくね。\r\n\r\n明石（あかし）は日本海軍唯一の新造工作艦。艦名